    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean yeah i get there's two sides but like, if u look at the actual trend lines from the last 10 years, isn't it pretty clear that as benefits went up, participation dropped? it feels like one side of that argument is way more backed by the recent data than the other.",
